    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the upholstery is clean and intact, showing only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and mechanical systems are fully functional, and the car drives smoothly. It is a solid, honest example of this model that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate work.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
